1
00:00:32,044 --> 00:00:35,415
=Love Actually S5=
(Extra Episode)

2
00:00:35,648 --> 00:00:41,080
(Back to the house)

3
00:00:41,080 --> 00:00:41,959
What did you just want?

4
00:00:42,520 --> 00:00:43,360
Do you need something?

5
00:00:44,799 --> 00:00:45,560
I don't.

6
00:00:45,560 --> 00:00:47,119
I'm just checking if the rice
has started cooking.

7
00:00:48,080 --> 00:00:49,119
No, I don't need anything.

8
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:51,439
Do you need any help?

9
00:00:51,439 --> 00:00:52,040
No, thanks.

10
00:00:52,040 --> 00:00:52,599
Don't worry about it.

11
00:00:54,240 --> 00:00:57,200
Then I'll just stir-fry the eggs, onion,
and tomato

12
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:58,279
all together.

13
00:00:58,279 --> 00:00:59,200
Yes, that's exactly what I mean.

14
00:00:59,680 --> 00:01:00,439
Like a hodgepodge.

15
00:01:01,159 --> 00:01:03,040
Okay, we'll take turns being the chef.

16
00:01:04,559 --> 00:01:06,199
You know, there's a pattern
in dating variety shows.

17
00:01:06,199 --> 00:01:07,400
The chef never finds love.

18
00:01:09,919 --> 00:01:10,400
Really?

19
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:13,040
The chef never finds love.

20
00:01:13,040 --> 00:01:14,519
He's whisking the eggs right now.

21
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:19,040
I cooked a few days ago.

22
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,239
It's okay.

23
00:01:20,239 --> 00:01:21,120
Everyone just...

24
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:21,959
I cooked too.

25
00:01:21,959 --> 00:01:22,160
Right.

26
00:01:22,160 --> 00:01:24,319
We all take turns together, so...

27
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:27,519
So just stay out of the kitchen.

28
00:01:29,519 --> 00:01:30,279
But I think

29
00:01:30,279 --> 00:01:32,919
friendship is the most important
thing here.

30
00:01:32,919 --> 00:01:35,120
You're absolutely right.

31
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:36,760
Because I think love

32
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:38,199
includes friendship.

33
00:01:38,432 --> 00:01:39,480
(Deeply agree)

34
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:40,440
Romantic love and friendship.

35
00:01:40,440 --> 00:01:41,319
Friendship is just

36
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:42,760
a very small part of love.

37
00:01:43,199 --> 00:01:44,800
Human beings have a great love.

38
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:46,760
Love for the Earth, for animals.

39
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:49,559
That's so well said.

40
00:01:52,040 --> 00:01:53,000
Let me cook tomorrow.

41
00:01:55,639 --> 00:01:56,800
We'll just have one dish?

42
00:01:58,599 --> 00:02:00,360
I'll come and help too.

43
00:02:05,879 --> 00:02:06,519
I'm coming.

44
00:02:07,199 --> 00:02:08,080
What are you doing, Ruita?

45
00:02:08,559 --> 00:02:09,440
