Don't be like this.

50
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,800
Let go.

51
00:02:17,024 --> 00:02:18,816
(Should I take this or not?)

52
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:20,000
Don't be like this.

53
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,520
- Don't be like this.
- Don't be like this.

54
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,119
Don't be like this.

55
00:02:23,119 --> 00:02:24,399
I'll be unhappy if you keep this up.

56
