for that karaoke app.

82
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:31,039
Bluetooth mode.

83
00:03:31,039 --> 00:03:31,880
It matches this.

84
00:03:32,839 --> 00:03:33,199
That's perfect.

85
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,160
That's perfect.

86
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:41,000
Pick.

87
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:42,479
Pick a song.

88
00:03:43,119 --> 00:03:44,000
Pick

89
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:45,960
"Empty World".

90
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:48,600
"The One And Only" is also fine.

91
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:54,039
Who'll sing?

92
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:54,399
You.

93
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:55,639
Come on.

94
00:03:57,919 --> 00:03:59,559
