96
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,839
The mic is a bit low.

97
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:07,000
Can't tell, but...

98
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:10,320
But this microphone...

99
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:13,080
There can't be a better microphone.

100
00:04:14,160 --> 00:04:15,639
Unless we buy some.

101
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:18,679
I actually have one at home.

102
00:04:22,239 --> 00:04:24,239
Let's go and see how their cooking
is going.

103
00:04:24,239 --> 00:04:25,279
I feel like the scrambled eggs
with tomatoes

104
00:04:25,279 --> 00:04:26,839
