105
00:04:32,839 --> 00:04:34,079
It's about to turn golden, right?

106
00:04:34,631 --> 00:04:35,239
(The chef is cooking.)

107
00:04:35,239 --> 00:04:36,320
- It smells so good.
- It smells great.

108
00:04:37,559 --> 00:04:38,480
Scrambled eggs with tomatoes.

109
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,200
CCTV.

110
