Huh, Danqi?

117
00:04:58,839 --> 00:04:59,440
What?

118
00:05:00,119 --> 00:05:02,119
She said when pretending to speak
like a Beijinger,

119
00:05:02,119 --> 00:05:03,600
"xi hong shi chao ji dan"
[*Scrambled eggs with tomatoes]

120
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,359
is "Xiong shi chao ji dan".
[*Chest is scrambled eggs]

121
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:06,839
"Xiong shi chao ji dan".
[*Chest is scrambled eggs]

122
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:07,559
"Xi hong shi chao ji dan".
[*Scrambled eggs with tomatoes]

123
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,559
Tomatoes.

124
00:05:09,559 --> 00:05:10,679
Tomatoes.

125
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,359
Queen of bad jokes.

126
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:13,920
That's a good one.

127
00:05:24,359 --> 00:05:25,519
Hello.

128
00:05:25,519 --> 00:05:26,279
Are you busy?

129
00:05:26,279 --> 00:05:28,359
When I saw the messages blowing up,

130
00:05:28,359 --> 00:05:29,399
I got a bit anxious.

131
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:31,359
Okay.

132
00:05:31,359 --> 00:05:33,440
Then just watch quietly by yourself.

133
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:35,799
Is our food almost ready?

134
00:05:36,880 --> 00:05:37,799
I'll call you when it's ready.

135
00:05:37,799 --> 00:05:38,239
Thanks.

136
00:05:39,799 --> 00:05:41,640
Aren't you guys eating?

137
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:42,160
We are.

138
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,200
Don't keep this leftover one.

139
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:43,839
That's amazing.

140
00:05:46,912 --> 00:05:47,584
(Tasty)

141
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:49,160
I need to get some too.

142
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:50,880
