143
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:52,679
It's good, delicious.

144
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,359
The king oyster mushrooms are so good.

145
00:05:55,359 --> 00:05:57,024
Perfect, really delicious.

146
00:05:57,024 --> 00:05:57,679
Delicious.

147
00:05:58,559 --> 00:05:59,160
Very flavorful.

148
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:01,119
So delicious.

149
00:06:02,119 --> 00:06:04,040
Where's a charging port here?

150
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:05,880
Go look in the living room.

151
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:06,640
Over here.

152
00:06:06,640 --> 00:06:07,799
Lizheng, there's food over there.

153
00:06:10,279 --> 00:06:10,760
So, Xiaowen,

154
00:06:10,760 --> 00:06:11,760
when did you start

155
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:12,959
