159
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:19,440
I could cook before,

160
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:20,600
but it was just...

161
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,239
Okay,

162
00:06:21,239 --> 00:06:22,839
but to become a chef is still...

163
00:06:22,839 --> 00:06:23,839
I'm not a chef.

164
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:24,799
Chef.

165
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:28,320
Amazing.

166
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,040
What's wrong?

167
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:38,679
What's wrong?

168
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:43,320
I dropped something on the lawn.

169
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:45,160
What is it?

170
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:46,480
What is it?

171
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,200
It's just...

172
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:51,160
