Because we were sitting right there.

178
00:07:13,720 --> 00:07:14,920
Did you find it?

179
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:19,760
What kind of thing is it?

180
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:20,880
Jewelry?

181
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:24,079
It's okay.

182
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:30,440
Who exactly? Is it me?

183
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:32,279
Your phone probably
automatically connected to that speaker.

184
00:07:32,912 --> 00:07:35,552
(The ring from Ling Lizheng)

185
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,640
I'm so frustrated.

186
00:07:41,640 --> 00:07:42,920
It's okay.

187
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:44,399
There will be new ones.

188
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:47,480
I'm sorry.

189
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,640
It's okay.

190
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,119
- I'm really sorry.
- There will be new ones.

191
00:07:50,119 --> 00:07:50,640
It's okay.

192
00:07:53,399 --> 00:07:54,760
(I could see she was very anxious.)

193
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:56,200
(The only thing I could do
was comfort her.)

194
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:58,559
It's fine.

195
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,440
Come, come sit down.

196
00:08:01,119 --> 00:08:01,920
Don't squat.

197
00:08:03,959 --> 00:08:05,399
I'm contacting them urgently.

198
00:08:06,959 --> 00:08:09,160
It's just an object.

199
00:08:09,799 --> 00:08:10,359
Don't take it...

200
00:08:19,359 --> 00:08:19,760
What is it?

201
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:20,839
I didn't see you with anything.

202
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:24,359
Is it something very valuable?

203
00:08:24,359 --> 00:08:24,576
No.

204
00:08:24,576 --> 00:08:25,472
Not valuable.

205
00:08:25,472 --> 00:08:26,160
What is it?

206
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,440
Is it something very valuable?

207
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:30,320
No, it's my own thing.

208
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:31,160
Personal item?

209
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:34,679
It's okay. Don't be too anxious.

210
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,520
It's okay. Don't be too anxious.

211
00:08:43,232 --> 00:08:44,479
Are you worried you can't find it?

212
00:08:44,479 --> 00:08:45,039
Yes.

213
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:46,560
No, it will be found.

214
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:51,400
Worried.

215
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:52,719
Are you worried you can't find it?

216
00:08:52,719 --> 00:08:53,919
- Yes, I'm worried I can't find it.
- No.

217
00:08:53,919 --> 00:08:54,880
It'll be found.

218
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:55,880
That's funny.

219
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:56,760
It'll be found.

220
00:08:56,760 --> 00:08:57,960
Okay.

221
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:04,799
Let me.

222
00:09:04,799 --> 00:09:05,799
I'm just right here.

223
00:09:05,799 --> 00:09:06,719
Thank you.

224
00:09:06,719 --> 00:09:08,119
- I'll help you.
- Don't wash them.

225
00:09:08,119 --> 00:09:08,559
Let me wash them.

226
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:11,239
No worries. I'm just right here.

227
00:09:11,239 --> 00:09:12,599
Sit for a while.

228
00:09:12,599 --> 00:09:13,599
Don't fight me for it.

229
00:09:13,599 --> 00:09:14,359
I'm really going to wash them.

230
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:17,320
Want to do some work?

231
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,760
Yes, I want to work.

232
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:20,000
Right now, I really want to work.

233
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:21,440
Okay.

234
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:22,479
So,

235
00:09:23,159 --> 00:09:25,359
