to release your emotions.

236
00:09:25,359 --> 00:09:26,960
Yes, just work.

237
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:27,559
I support you.

238
00:09:27,559 --> 00:09:28,119
Burying yourself in work.

239
00:09:28,119 --> 00:09:28,719
Right.

240
00:09:28,719 --> 00:09:29,520
Okay.

241
00:09:43,359 --> 00:09:43,960
I'm leaving.

242
00:09:44,320 --> 00:09:45,400
Good luck at work, bye-bye.

243
00:09:46,251 --> 00:09:51,168
(Everyone is heading out to work
one after another)

244
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:57,840
We're all in black, the three of us.

245
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:58,520
Right?

246
00:09:58,880 --> 00:09:59,479
Yes.

247
00:10:00,119 --> 00:10:00,799
I'm in black too.

248
00:10:00,799 --> 00:10:02,000
Look, if I tie this on,

249
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:03,840
- I'm in black too.
- It's a sea of black in the mirror.

250
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:04,119
This way,

251
00:10:04,119 --> 00:10:04,679
the four of us

252
00:10:04,679 --> 00:10:06,200
