258
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:14,799
So cool.

259
00:10:14,799 --> 00:10:15,119
Cool.

260
00:10:17,559 --> 00:10:18,400
Pretty cool.

261
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:18,919
Really cool.

262
00:10:18,919 --> 00:10:21,520
I like this.

263
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:22,840
Please send me this photo.

264
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,392
This is awesome.

265
00:10:23,392 --> 00:10:23,880
Too cool.

266
00:10:28,719 --> 00:10:29,640
Well, Danqi.

267
00:10:29,640 --> 00:10:30,048
