274
00:10:39,479 --> 00:10:40,599
Intellectual black.

275
00:10:41,239 --> 00:10:41,719
Intellectual black.

276
00:10:41,719 --> 00:10:42,280
Right?

277
00:10:42,280 --> 00:10:43,479
