279
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:47,200
You, you are fully mature.

280
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,128
We are semi-mature.

281
00:10:48,128 --> 00:10:49,400
Put you on the grill.

282
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:51,159
You'll be fully mature soon.
[*Homophonic to "fully cooked"]

283
00:10:51,616 --> 00:10:52,960
